page.title: 12Health Services
page.content: In Tayport there are five{doctor's}and one trainee who share a group practice with a nearby town.In the doctor's there are two surgeries, three receptionist's and a waiting room. Also in Tayport there is a health clinic in which there is a surgery for the{dentist,}a surgery for the{doctor and a room for the{chiropodist.}Also in the clinic there is a communal waiting room for the{dentist}there is a dental{hygienist}who come's once a month and for the{doctor}there are four district{nurse's. } Tayport is also served by one {dentist}who has two surgeries,one nurse,one receptionist and a waiting room.The{dentist}is also served by a visiting{hygienist. The nearest{hospital}is 7km away,in Dundee.
